{
  "texts": [
    "How would you place your views on this scale, generally speaking?\"",
    "The scale ranges from 1 (\"left\") to 10 (\"right\").",
    "The other items were chosen because they are available in all waves, cover core areas of sociological inquiry and include opinions as well as attitudes.",
    "Social trust (e.g.",
    "Schilke et al., 2021) is measured with the question \"Generally speaking, would you say that most people can be trusted or that you need to be very careful in dealing with people?"
  ]
}